8, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2013_BNP_Paribas_Open\", \"score\": 0.9999999975798346, \"rank\": 2.4202005767191267e-09, \"text\": \"BNP Paribas\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2013_BNP_Paribas_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2013_BNP_Paribas_Open\"}, {\"begin\": 2039, \"end\": 2053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Team_Cup\", \"score\": 0.9997299016591766, \"rank\": 0.0002701713114559986, \"text\": \"World Team Cup\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Team_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Team_Cup\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the quads event, two-time Grand Slam champion Donald Ramphadi, ranked world No 4, is set to make his Paralympic debut.\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He begins his journey against Brazil's Leandro Pena, the world No 13.\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2265, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2226, \"end\": 2232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9990985468016853, \"rank\": 0.0009001888235956775, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A potential second-round clash with Dutch top seed Sam Schroder looms large if Ramphadi advances.\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2364, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2303, \"end\": 2308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999158185510826, \"rank\": 4.401450055067014e-05, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 2318, \"end\": 2321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.8854212979991591, \